## Technical Architecture

### [markdownService.ts](file:///Users/danielbergholz/Documents/Second%20Brain/00.%20Attachments/06.%20Antigravity/LIfe-RPG/services/markdownService.ts) (The Eye)
*   **Function**: Scans your vault using Obsidian's `MetadataCache`.
*   **Logic**:
    *   Detects "Daily Notes" via liberal pattern matching (`YYYY-MM-DD`, [Daily/](file:///Users/danielbergholz/Documents/Second%20Brain/00.%20Attachments/06.%20Antigravity/LIfe-RPG/types.ts#81-86) folder).
    *   Extracts frontmatter keys (`Brush_Teeth:: 2`) for habit tracking.
    *   Calculates "Effort XP" based on `file.stat.size` (capped at 500xp/file).
    *   **Performance**: Event-driven (only reparses on `metadata:changed`).

### [persistenceService.ts](file:///Users/danielbergholz/Documents/Second%20Brain/00.%20Attachments/06.%20Antigravity/LIfe-RPG/services/persistenceService.ts) (The Memory)
*   **Function**: Manages the `life-rpg-data.json` file in your vault root.
*   **Data**: Stores your custom Settings, Layout state, and History.

### [HomeBase.tsx](file:///Users/danielbergholz/Documents/Second%20Brain/00.%20Attachments/06.%20Antigravity/LIfe-RPG/components/HomeBase.tsx) (The View)
*   **Function**: Renders the Zen Garden.
*   **Tech**: React + Canvas-style div positioning. Uses a procedural noise map for terrain generation.

### [App.tsx](file:///Users/danielbergholz/Documents/Second%20Brain/00.%20Attachments/06.%20Antigravity/LIfe-RPG/App.tsx) (The Controller)
*   **Function**: The main React container mounted into the Obsidian Leaf. Handles tab switching and global state.

